<p>Ok, run <code>search.feature</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./vendor/bin/behat features/web/search.feature</div></code></pre>
<p>It fails for a completely different reason. Things are never boring here! This is
a unique constraint violation because it's not clearing out the data before loading
the fixtures. This is a funny edge case. Because the new <code>@BeforeScenario</code> is near
the top and the other for clearing the data is lower, they're being run in that order.
Move these <code>@BeforeScenarios</code> up top and keep them in the order that you want:</p>
